incident_updates.body:
Our teams are continue to work on this issue.
Most of the impacted servers have been brought back up.
We are focusing on the remaining ones.
The incident is always handled by our teams, who strive to return the services to you as soon as possible.

Our technical teams are still hands on the issue.
Update will be post as significant progress is made.

Start time : 17/10/2022 10:00 UTC Service impact : Some servers in the rack R807L27 are over-heating or no longer responding. Ongoing actions : Our teams are investigating to determine the origin of the incident and fix it.

Estimated time to recovery : 1 hour(s)
Affected hosts
host1048597.sbg8.cloud.ovh.net
